  "instructions": [
    "Heat the vegetable shortening in a cazuela over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion and garlic, saut\u007f until softened, about 2 minutes.",
    "Add the apple cider vinegar, Dijon mustard, water, carrots, potatoes, thyme, salt, and pepper.",
    "Stir to combine, then reduce heat to low and simmer, covered, for 45 minutes, or until the vegetables are tender.",
    "Add the bacon fat and stir to combine.",
    "Continue to simmer, uncovered, for an additional 15 minutes, or until the sauce has thickened slightly.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with additional thyme, if desired."
